Package enquiry

Class Enquiry

java.lang.Object
enquiry.Enquiry
public class Enquiry extends Object
The Enquiry class represents a user's inquiry about a specific camp. It contains information about the enquirer, the creation date, and any replies.
Since:
2023-11-13
Version:
1.4
Author:
Wang Jing
